text.tspan: In today’s fast-paced operational landscape, efficient fleet management has become a cornerstone of modern
logistics and transportation systems. The ability to monitor, maintain, and optimize a fleet not only improves
productivity but also ensures safety, cost-effectiveness, and sustainability. Through the integration of digital
technologies, organizations can now gain real-time insights into vehicle performance, driver behavior, and operational
efficiency — transforming traditional fleet operations into data-driven, intelligent ecosystems.
